### Test API Endpoints
### Sử dụng REST Client extension trong VS Code để test

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ==================== AUTH ====================

### Sign Up
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "candidate@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "userData": {
    "full_name": "John Doe",
    "role": "candidate"
  }
}

### Sign In
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "candidate@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Sign Out
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== JOBS ====================

### Get All Jobs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs?page=1&limit=10

### Get All Jobs with Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs?search=developer&location=Hanoi

### Get Job by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/job-uuid-here

### Create Job (Recruiter)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "recruiter_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "title": "Senior Full Stack Developer",
  "description": "We are looking for an experienced Full Stack Developer...",
  "requirements": "5+ years of experience with React and Node.js",
  "location": "Ho Chi Minh City",
  "job_type": "full-time",
  "salary_min": 30000000,
  "salary_max": 50000000,
  "status": "active"
}

### Update Job
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/job-uuid-here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Senior Full Stack Developer (Updated)",
  "salary_max": 60000000
}

### Delete Job
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/jobs/job-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================== APPLICATIONS ====================

### Get All Applications
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/applications

### Get Applications by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/applications?userId=user-uuid-here

### Get Applications by Job
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/applications?jobId=job-uuid-here

### Get Application by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/application-uuid-here

### Submit Application
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/applications
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "job_id": "job-uuid-here",
  "user_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "resume_url": "https://example.com/resume.pdf",
  "cover_letter": "I am very interested in this position...",
  "answers": {
    "question1": "Answer 1",
    "question2": "Answer 2"
  }
}

### Update Application Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/applications/application-uuid-here/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "interview"
}

### ==================== PROFILES ====================

### Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles/user-uuid-here

### Update User Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles/user-uuid-here
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "full_name": "John Doe Updated",
  "phone": "+84123456789",
  "location": "Ho Chi Minh City",
  "bio": "Experienced software developer...",
  "skills": ["JavaScript", "React", "Node.js"]
}

### ==================== MESSAGES ====================

### Get Conversations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/messages/conversations?userId=user-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Messages in Conversation
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/messages/conversation-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send Message
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "conversation_id": "conversation-uuid-here",
  "sender_id": "user-uuid-here",
  "content": "Hello, I have a question about the job..."
}

### ==================== ANALYTICS ====================

### Get Recruiter Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/analytics/recruiter/recruiter-uuid-here
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
